}}'''Snaptube'''是一款智能手机应用程序，用户可以通過Snaptube从[[YouTube|YouTube]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[Instagram|Instagram]]、[[WhatsApp|WhatsApp]]、[[Snapchat|Snapchat]]等来源下载视频和音乐<ref>{{Cite press release|agency=[[Asian_News_International|Asian News International]]|language=en|accessdate=2020-03-09}}</ref>。Snaptube于2014年发布。2019年，安全研究人员发现，该应用在用户不知情的情况下，在用户的手机上进行欺诈活动（例如点击欺诈以及在用户不知情的情况下订阅<ref>{{Cite web|title=Popular app Snaptube accused of ad fraud, say researchers|url=http://social.techcrunch.com/2019/10/17/snaptube-invisible-ads-ad-fraud-charging-premium/|accessdate=2020-03-08|author=Whittaker|date=17 October 2019|first=Zack|work=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Secure-D uncovers non-human clicks and subscriptions from popular Android app Snaptube|url=https://www.upstreamsystems.com/secure-d-uncovers-non-human-clicks-subscriptions-popular-android-app-snaptube/|accessdate=2020-03-09|date=2019-10-17|work=Upstream|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520153015/https://www.upstreamsystems.com/secure-d-uncovers-non-human-clicks-subscriptions-popular-android-app-snaptube/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=This Android app with 40 million downloads 'robbing' users - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/gadgets-news/this-android-app-with-40-million-users-robbing-users/articleshow/71687656.cms|accessdate=2020-03-09|work=The Times of India|archive-date=2019-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022150222/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/gadgets-news/this-android-app-with-40-million-users-robbing-users/articleshow/71687656.cms}}</ref>）。安全研究人员从该应用中发现了超过7000万次可疑交易请求<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fraud alert: Popular video app Snaptube needs careful watching|url=https://www.upstreamsystems.com/fraud-alert-popular-video-app-snaptube-needs-careful-watching/|accessdate=2020-03-09|date=2019-10-17|work=Upstream|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115022113/https://www.upstreamsystems.com/fraud-alert-popular-video-app-snaptube-needs-careful-watching/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=IF YOU HAVE “SNAPTUBE” ON YOUR PHONE, ITS TIME TO UNINSTALL IT|url=https://www.gizchina.com/2019/10/28/if-you-have-snaptube-on-your-phone-its-time-to-uninstall-it/amp/|accessdate=2020-12-14|date=2019-10-28|work=gizchina|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114212547/https://www.gizchina.com/2019/10/28/if-you-have-snaptube-on-your-phone-its-time-to-uninstall-it/amp/}}</ref>。在[[谷歌|谷歌]]将该应用从[[Google_Play_Store|Google Play Store]]下架后，开发者Mobiuspace将责任归咎于一个名为 "Mango SDK "的第三方软件开发工具包，开发者声称已经删除了违规的[[SDK|SDK]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=[Update: Rogue third-party SDK removed] Snaptube caught with ad click fraud scheme and unwanted subscription signups|url=https://www.androidpolice.com/2019/10/23/snaptube-click-fraud-subscriptions/|accessdate=2020-03-09|date=2019-10-23|work=Android Police|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520160339/https://www.androidpolice.com/2019/10/23/snaptube-click-fraud-subscriptions/}}</ref>。用戶仍可通過Aptoide等商店下載Snaptube。

